data.description: This beautiful home in the heart of Converse is perfect for a growing family and has plenty of room for all your loved ones to be comfortable. Boasting a recently updated interior with: All black granite kitchen counters, grey LVP flooring throughout, Recent AC (12 months old), Rainfall shower head in master, and only a 8 year old roof ! Living in Northampton puts you in the middle of it all...Shopping, dining, entertainment, and easy access to major freeways. Minutes from both Randolph AFB, and Fort Sam Houston, the neighborhood amenities include the community pool, clubhouse, park and playground right down the road. Come check out this gorgeous home and make it your own.
